&lt;li&gt;You would work with big data in our global data warehouse, so keeping an eye on a report performance is a must.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You would support managers and their enquiries – you would make sure they can focus on the business using your reports and provided data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You would analyze data to identify trends and processes that could be automated.&lt;/li&gt;
